            <div type="transcript" id="F700A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Way I read a Letter's - this -</l>
                    <l>'Tis first - I lock the Door - </l>
                    <l>And push it with my<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 fingers - next - </l>
                    <l>For transport it be sure - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And then I go the furthest off</l>
                    <l>To counteract a knock - </l>
                    <l>Then draw my little Letter forth </l>
                    <l>And<add type="alternate" extent="slowly">slily &amp;#x2022; softly</add>
 slowly pick the lock - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Then - glancing narrow, at the Wall - </l>
                    <l>And narrow at the<add type="alternate" extent="floor">door</add>
 floor</l>
                    <l>For firm Conviction of a Mouse </l>
                    <l>Not exorcised before - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Peruse how infinite I am </l>
                    <l>To no one that You - know - </l>
                    <l>And sigh for lack of Heaven -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 but not</l>
                    <l>The Heaven God bestow - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
